snippet.title: The Amber Room: Imperial Russia's Priceless Art Installation
snippet.description:
Do: use 10,000 pounds of amber to create a stunning golden room.

Do not: use amber (in any amount) to treat infantile teething.

I mean... we're not doctors, but this seems pretty obvious.
